00:10:09,692 --> 00:10:12,526
displaced mid-shaft
radius and ulna fractures.

246
00:10:12,595 --> 00:10:15,113
Yep. Well, Emily, unfortunately,

247
00:10:15,181 --> 00:10:16,592
your arm definitely
needs surgery.

248
00:10:16,616 --> 00:10:18,416
Now, in order to
stabilize the fracture,

249
00:10:18,451 --> 00:10:20,918
