in a plate and some screws.

250
00:10:20,987 --> 00:10:22,787
Uh, Edwards, call up to the OR.

251
00:10:22,856 --> 00:10:24,684
How long will it take to heal?

252
00:10:24,708 --> 00:10:27,069
