to cook, to train for school.

253
00:10:27,093 --> 00:10:28,787
Applications are due in a month.

254
00:10:28,811 --> 00:10:31,746
Well, obviously, it's a pretty
bad fracture, but we will fix you up,

255
00:10:31,814 --> 00:10:33,475
we will get you into
PT as soon as we can,

256
00:10:33,499 --> 00:10:35,783
and you will be back at it
