developed in two separate pieces.

261
00:10:48,148 --> 00:10:50,159
I'm sorry, but I thought you
said you could fix the gap.

262
00:10:50,183 --> 00:10:51,226
When is that gonna happen?

263
00:10:51,250 --> 00:10:52,933
Well, unfortunately,
Lee's images

264
00:10:53,002 --> 00:10:54,935
show a longer gap
