309
00:12:32,068 --> 00:12:33,562
Oh, he's such a lightweight.

310
00:12:33,586 --> 00:12:35,987
Well, hopefully, he's
buying you some chocolate.

311
00:12:36,055 --> 00:12:37,905
You're late.

312
00:12:37,973 --> 00:12:39,284
I'm so sorry. Uh, I was
checking on a baby in the NICU...

313
00:12:39,308 --> 00:12:41,409
Don't care.
Graham, start talking.

314
00:12:41,478 --> 00:12:43,494
Jaclyn Werlein,
23 weeks along...

315
00:12:43,563 --> 00:12:45,574
Recent fetal echo
of her baby's heart

316
00:12:45,598 --> 00:12:47,443
