critical aortic stenosis.

317
00:12:47,467 --> 00:12:50,101
Today, we'll be performing
a fetal aortic valvuloplasty

318
00:12:50,170 --> 00:12:52,202
in order to open up the
narrowed aortic valve.

319
00:12:52,272 --> 00:12:54,489
Your BP's a little
high. You feeling okay?

320
00:12:54,558 --> 00:12:56,207
I'm a little nervous.

321
00:12:56,275 --> 00:12:57,870
The idea of a giant
needle going through me

322
00:12:57,894 --> 00:13:00,261
