in the precise position

331
00:13:18,314 --> 00:13:20,131
that he needs to be. - Okay.

332
00:13:20,200 --> 00:13:22,328
Position is critical to success.

333
00:13:22,352 --> 00:13:24,752
If the fetus isn't facing
forward, chest up,

334
00:13:24,820 --> 00:13:26,748
