381
00:15:12,028 --> 00:15:15,128
How old is David?
Thirty-three, two kids and a wife.

382
00:15:15,197 --> 00:15:17,465
How long will a
replacement last?

383
00:15:17,533 --> 00:15:19,199
Uh, 10, 15 years.

384
00:15:19,268 --> 00:15:21,436
So, he'll need
another one eventually.

385
00:15:21,504 --> 00:15:24,100
Well, yeah, but we either
resect it and do a total hip now,

386
00:15:24,124 --> 00:15:26,791
or his cancer continues
to spread, and he dies.

387
00:15:26,860 --> 00:15:29,338
Well, it looks like I'm
scheduling a hip replacement.

388
00:15:29,362 --> 00:15:30,962
Yeah. Oh, no.

389
00:15:31,030 --> 00:15:32,713
Don't schedule
it now. I have a...

390
00:15:32,782 --> 00:15:34,114
